==Organizers== * Kokuryō Residents’ Association & Kokuryō Minazuki Festival Executive Committee= ==Sponsors== =* Kasuga Branch, Tamba City Chamber of Commerce* Kokuryō Shopping District ==Gallery== <gallery widths="180" heights="120">2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8564.JPG|People heading to the festival2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8726.JPG|Lantern floating on the Takeda River2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8597.JPG|Town center2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8620.JPG|Town center2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8635.JPG|Festival venue center2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8659.JPG|Outskirts of town2015-07-31Minazuki-Festival Kokuryo,Tamba,Hyogo-Japan 国領水無月祭り 8580.JPG|Kokuryō River, a tributary</gallery> ==References== {{Reflist}} ==See Also== {{Commonscat|Kokuryō Minazuki Matsuri}} * {{ill|Riverside festival|ja|川裾祭|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Ayabe Minazuki Festival|ja|あやべ水無月まつり|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Atago Festival (Tamba)|ja|愛宕祭 (丹波市)|qq=draft}}]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]]
