d bus and get off at "Shinshūkō-mae." * '''By Car:''' **About 8 minutes from {{ill|Kasuga Interchange|ja|春日インターチェンジ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kasuga Interchange|qq=}} on the [[:en:Maizuru-Wakasa Expressway|Maizuru-Wakasa Expressway]].
